Intimate Nature: Plants and Landscapes o.name: Intimate Nature: Plants and Landscapes of Central California Paintings by Jeanne Rosen Sofen
Intimate Nature: Plants and Landscapes o.venue: San Francisco Botanical Gardens (Helen Crocker Russell Library)
Intimate Nature: Plants and Landscapes o.description: Using a variety of painting techniques, Jeanne Rosen Sofen has created a loving tribute to the beauty and diversity of Central California, from Sierra Nevada mountains to oak woodlands, to coastal hills and redwoods. A lifetime of enjoying and observing the natural world combined with years of exploring painting techniques has brought us this exciting exhibit of paintings of plants and landscapes.
